| column_0 | column_1 | column_2 |
+----------+----------+----------+
|        3 |        1 |        5 |
|        2 |        2 |        4 |
|        1 |        3 |        3 |
|        2 |        2 |        2 |
|        3 |        1 |        1 |
+----------+----------+----------+

